</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-83_ pf-text-1">Do not apply ointments, butter, or ice to the burn, as these can worsen the injury.


























</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-85_ pf-r pf-c-lm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-86_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-cXPBhi kkWDYP pf-87_ pf-heading-1-h3">Prevention</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-89_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-90_ pf-text-1">Keep hot liquids out of reach, and never leave children unattended near heat sources or open flames.



















</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-92_ pf-text-1">Install smoke alarms and develop a family fire escape plan to prevent burn injuries at home.




























